{"step_index":136,"source":"MODEL","type":"PLANNER_RESPONSE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-06-12T15:02:39Z","content":"I have scaffolded out the complete architecture and infrastructure for **1V1 by Veritasco**, establishing the foundation for a production-ready, scalable, and fully functional competitive coding platform!\n\nGiven the massive scope of the project, I have implemented the core engine, backend schema, and services integration first. Here is what I have built for you:\n\n### 1. Complete Project & Folder Structure\nI set up the **Next.js 15 App Router** environment using TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and ESLint, strictly following modern best practices. The project is fully configured and ready.\n\n### 2. Full Prisma Schema (20+ Models)\nI translated your entire design into a robust `prisma/schema.prisma` file, including tables for:\n*   **Users & Profiles**: `User`, `Account`, `Session`, `VerificationToken`\n*   **Matchmaking**: `Match`, `MatchPlayer`\n*   **Coding Problems**: `Problem`, `TestCase`, `ProblemTag`, `Editorial`, `Submission`\n*   **Monetization**: `CoinTransaction`, `Payment`, `Subscription` (Razorpay ready)\n<truncated 2231 bytes>"}
{"step_index":137,"source":"USER_EXPLICIT","type":"USER_INPUT","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-06-12T15:05:46Z","content":"<USER_REQUEST>\nBUILD A COMPLETE PRODUCTION-READY WEB APPLICATION CALLED \"CODEDUEL\"\n\nPROJECT VISION\n\nCodeDuel is a real-time competitive coding platform where users battle each other by solving the same programming problem. The experience should feel like Chess.com + LeetCode + Clash Royale progression.\n\nThe platform must be scalable, modern, secure, mobile-friendly, and production-ready.\n\nTECH STACK\n\nFrontend:\n\n* Next.js 15 App Router\n* TypeScript\n* Tailwind CSS\n* Shadcn UI\n* Framer Motion\n* Monaco Editor\n\nBackend:\n\n* Next.js API Routes\n* Socket.IO\n* Redis\n* PostgreSQL\n* Prisma ORM\n\nAuthentication:\n\n* NextAuth\n* Google OAuth\n* GitHub OAuth\n* Email/Password Login\n* Password Reset\n\nCode Execution:\n\n* Judge0 CE\n\nPayments:\n\n* Razorpay\n* Subscription Support\n* Coin Purchase Support\n\nInfrastructure:\n\n* Docker\n* Docker Compose\n* Vercel Compatible\n* CI/CD Ready\n\n==================================================\n\nCORE GAMEPLAY\n\nUsers compete in coding battles.\n\nFlow:\n\n1. User clicks Find Match\n2. Matchmaking starts\n<truncated 8942 bytes>"}
